<plot>After pulling off his last job as a safe-cracker, Ravi decides he has had enough and decides to go straight. He gets a job looking after wood products as a manager with the owner, and his daughter, Reena. Ravi cracks open a safe to save the daughter of the local police chief, winning respect and admiration from Reena and the entire community in general. Ravi and Reena then fall in love. Then Ravi gets a visit from his former crime partner, Robert and his girlfriend, Julie, who need his help in cracking open a safe they had robbed recently, and will not take no for an answer.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?020400</url></doc>
